.SH NAME
gmc-wt-switch - Interactively switch to another worktree


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBgmc wt switch [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
Interactively select a worktree and switch to it.

.PP
Requires shell integration. If not set up, run:
  eval "$(gmc wt init zsh)"  # or bash/fish

.PP
Without shell integration, this command will only print the path.


.SH OPTIONS
\fB-h\fP, \fB--help\fP[=false]
	help for switch


